==地理==

[[File:Sungai_Bone_dan_muaranya.jpg|thumb]]

哥伦打洛市面积66,25 km²，占全省面积的0.55%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gorontaloprov.go.id/profil/kondisi-geografis|title=Kondisi Geografis Provinsi Gorontalo|last=|first=|date=|website=www.gorontaloporv.go.id|publisher=|access-date=|quote=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130507091301/http://www.gorontaloprov.go.id/profil/kondisi-geografis|archivedate=2013-05-07}}</ref>，位于波尼河（[[印尼语|印尼语]]：Sungai Bone）入海口处，东接[[波尼波朗戈县|波尼波朗戈县]]，西靠[[哥伦打洛县|哥伦打洛县]]，南滨哥伦打洛湾（[[印尼语|印尼语]]：Teluk Gorontalo）<ref group="注">哥伦打洛湾是[[托米尼湾|托米尼湾]]内的一个小海湾</ref>，城市西北即是哥伦打洛省的最大湖[[林博托湖|林博托湖]]。根据[[柯本气候分类法|柯本气候分类法]]，哥伦打洛属[[热带雨林气候|热带雨林气候]]（''Af''）<ref name="weatherbase">{{cite web |url=http://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weather-summary.php3?s=84079&cityname=Gorontalo%2C+Gorontalo%2C+Indonesia&units= |title=GORONTALO, INDONESIA |last= |first= |date= |website=www.weatherbase.com |publisher=weatherbase |access-date=2017-07-21 |quote= |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111191539/http://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weather-summary.php3?s=84079&cityname=Gorontalo%2C+Gorontalo%2C+Indonesia&units= |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref group="注">另一说哥伦打洛属[[热带季风气候|热带季风气候]]（''Am''）</ref><ref name="climate-data"></ref>，各月都有明显降水，旱季较短<ref name="climate-data"></ref>，年平均气温26.6℃，年均降水量1219.2 ㎜，最湿月和最干月降水差距为138 ㎜<ref name="climate-data">{{cite web |url=https://en.climate-data.org/location/627919/ |title=CLIMATE: GORONTALO |last= |first= |date= |website=climate-data.org |publisher= |access-date=2017-07-21 |quote=}}</ref>。

